trans-unit.source: Represents a service description format extension applied to a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Port"></xref> when an XML Web service supports the SOAP protocol version 1.2.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en beskrivelse format utvidelsen brukes på en <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Port"> </xref> når en XML-webtjeneste støtter SOAP-protokollversjon 1.2.

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hvordan du angir protokollene for XML-webtjenester [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices >]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om Web Services (WSDL = Description Language), kan du se spesifikasjonen på http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Soap12AddressBinding"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Soap12AddressBinding"> </xref> klasse.
